o review task reports, invoices, milestones, and audit trails. Execution logs are loaded on-demand and cached strictly in local transient memory.\n 88 |               </p>\n 89 |             </div>\n 90 | \n 91 |             {/* Block 2: Handshake / Decoupling Tunnel */}\n 92 |             <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4\">\n 93 |               <div className=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n 94 |                 <span className=\"h-[1px] flex-grow bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF]/30 to-[#E4000F]/30\" />\n 95 |                 <div className=\"px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-[9px] font-mono text-white/60 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n 96 |                   <Lock className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#E4000F]\" /> Zero-Trust Handshake\n 97 |                 </div>\n 98 |                 <span className=\"h-[1px] flex-grow bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4000F]/30 to-[#009DFF]/30\" />\n 99 |               </div>\n100 |               <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40 text-center max-w-[280px] font-mono leading-relaxed mt-2\">\n101 |                 AES-256 session token pathways keep client secrets invisible to presentation networks.\n102 |               </p>\n103 |             </div>\n104 | \n105 |             {/* Block 3: Live Sovereign Enclaves */}\n106 |             <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-md relative group\">\n107 |               <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-3 h-3 border-t border-r border-white/20 rounded-tr-2xl\" />\n108 |               <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\">\n109 |                 <div className=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-[#E4000F]/5 border border-[#E4000F]/20 flex items-center justify-center\">\n110 |                   <Server className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E4000F]\" />\n111 |                 </div>\n112 |                 <div>\n113 |                   <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Sovereign Model Enclaves</h4>\n114 |                   <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F]\">HYPERVISOR REINFORCED / eBPF</span>\n115 |                 </div>\n116 |               </div>\n117 |               <p className=\"text-[12.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light font-sans\">\n118 |                 The actual agent brains and workflows. Active model parameters, memory maps, and tool executables run in isolated enclaves protected by hardware seed security boundaries.\n119 |               </p>\n120 |             </div>\n121 | \n122 |           </div>\n123 |         </div>\n124 |       </section>\n125 | \n126 |       {/* 3. INTERACTIVE MODULE PREVIEW SYSTEM */}\n127 |       <section id=\"workspace-suite\" className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 py-20 lg:py-28 overflow-hidden\">\n128 |         <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto space-y-16\">\n129 |           \n130 |           {/* Section Heading */}\n131 |           <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-end border-b border-white/5 pb-8\">\n132 |             <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-4\">\n133 |               <span className=\"text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.15em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase\">\n134 |                 Interactive Suite Overview\n135 |               </span>\n136 |               <h2 className=\"text-[32px] sm:text-[44px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-none\">\n137 |                 The Sovereign Workspace Suite\n138 |               </h2>\n139 |               <p className=\"text-[14px] sm:text-[16px] text-white/60 font-light max-w-[640px] leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n140 |                 Explore each system module pre-integrated into our secure presentation layer. Click a module below to inspect real-time system behaviors, specifications, and simulated terminal outputs.\n141 |               </p>\n142 |             </div>\n143 |             <div className=\"lg:col-spa